messages.message: hey team, can anyone confirm for me that this document is accurate, and that the SDLC feature is only considering minor bugfixes at the moment? https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/CI/pages/1214185827/Third-party+Integrations#Git-SDLC-(maintenance-only)
Hi Ben, correct, we haven't done active SDLC development for quite some time and it is under maintenance mode if I understand correctly. @Heymian could comment more.

that is correct, we don’t actually have a sense of whether this is something that makes sense for us to support moving forward. no active development has happened here for a while so we shouldn’t encourage any customers to use this
